results.name: S2G 'Grey Black'
results.story: The adidas S2G ‘Grey Black’ brings sustainable running-shoe comfort to the golf course. In keeping with adidas’ commitment to eliminating plastic waste, part of the grey textile upper is made with 50% recycled content. A waterproof coating keeps feet dry when playing in wet conditions. adidas’ Bounce cushioning is utilized on the midsole, supported by a spikeless Adiwear outsole. A V-shaped Traxtion pattern yields superior grip on the green and versatile wear off the course.

results.name: Swarovski x Wmns Sambarose 'Cloud White'
results.story: An exclusive colorway made for Valentine’s Day, the Swarovski x adidas women’s Sambarose ‘Cloud White’ comes with a removable metallic gold charm encrusted with crystals. A subtle off-white finish is applied to the leather upper, modeled after the classic Samba and stamped with ‘Swarovski Crystals’ on the lateral heel in pink lettering. The same hue is repeated on zigzag stitching around the heel tab and an adidas Trefoil logo atop the tongue. A rubber platform midsole anchors the low-top.

results.name: S2G BOA 'Grey Solar Yellow'
results.story: The adidas S2G BOA ‘Grey Solar Yellow’ delivers a spikeless golf shoe that combines precision comfort with lightweight, flexible cushioning. A micro-adjustable BOA Fit System secures the grey textile upper, made in part with recycled polyester and coated in a waterproof polyurethane film. The streamlined build rests on a full-length Bounce midsole, supported underfoot by a durable Adiwear outsole with a V-shaped Traxion pattern designed to dig into turf.

results.name: Disney x Court Rallye Slip J 'Minnie Mouse'
Swarovski x Wmns Sambarose 'Core Black'
results.story: Launching as part of a Valentine’s Day-themed capsule collection, the Swarovski x adidas women’s Sambarose ‘Core Black’ treats the retro-inspired silhouette to a luxe makeover. The black leather low-top is mounted on an exaggerated midsole and accessorized with a removable metallic gold charm, its gleaming surface encrusted with Swarovski crystals. The atelier gets a callout on the sneaker’s lateral heel, stamped in blue lettering that matches the zigzag stitching around the heel tab.

results.name: Swarovski x Wmns Sambarose 'White Clear Aqua'
results.story: The Swarovski x adidas women’s Sambarose ‘White Clear Aqua’ delivers a luxe take on the retro-inspired platform sneaker, highlighted by a removable Trefoil charm encrusted with Swarovski crystals. The off-white leather upper is accented a metallic silver heel tab and translucent turquoise three-stripes. The latter hue is repeated on tongue tag and a Swarovski Crystals wordmark on the lateral heel. Zigzag stitching outlines the signature T-toe, a detail that gives the nod to the original Samba.

results.name: EQT Primegreen 'Grey Sub Green'
results.story: The adidas EQT Primegreen ‘Grey Sub Green’ brings running shoe comfort to the golf course. Grey textile and matching synthetic leather overlays make up the composition of the waterproof upper, which incorporates recycled materials under the Primegreen banner. The sneaker rides on a lightweight Bounce midsole, enhanced with a Boost insert in the heel for improved impact absorption. Underfoot, the spikeless Adiwear outsole provides grippy traction on slippery greens.

results.name: ZX 10000 'Off White'
results.story: The adidas ZX 10000 ‘Off White’ brings back a vintage running silhouette from the brand’s late ‘80s archive. This one-to-one reissue features breathable white mesh construction with synthetic suede overlays in neutral black, grey and off-white tones. Shiny nylon is utilized on the toe box and heel tab, the latter finished in a neon green hue. The sneaker sits atop an off-white EVA midsole, supported by a decoupled rubber outsole stabilized with adidas’ Torsion bar.

results.name: Wmns Superstar Bold 'Heart Embossed - Scarlet'
results.story: The adidas women’s Superstar Bold ‘Heart Embossed’ delivers a fashion-forward take on the shell-toed silhouette, featuring exaggerated details and a platform midsole. A bold scarlet finish is applied to the leather upper, covered in a tonal print made up of alternating hearts and adidas Trefoils. Extra wide serrated three-stripes adorn the sneaker’s quarter panels, matching an enlarged heel tab marked with classic adidas branding. Heart-shaped eyelets and a heart-print sockliner amplify the sneaker’s romantic aesthetic.

results.name: Freak MD 'White Royal Blue'
results.story: The adidas Freak MD ‘White Royal Blue’ applies an eye-catching graphic print to the performance football cleat. The durable white synthetic upper is accented with a series of diagonal blue lines, joined by metallic three-stripes that shine on the lateral side panel. A padded mesh tongue provides breathable comfort. The lace-up rides on a lightweight and flexible Bounce midsole, reinforced by a cleated rubber outsole designed to grip the turf through every play.

results.name: Terrex Two Flow 'White Solar Yellow'
results.story: The adidas Terrex Two Flow ‘White Solar Yellow’ combines lightweight comfort with off-road traction. The minimalist upper is constructed from breathable textile, reinforced with translucent overlays and rendered in a blend of white and Solar Yellow. The latter hue is repeated on the Lightstrike midsole, offering plush cushioning with each step. Underfoot, a marbled black and white finish is applied to the Continental rubber outsole, equipped with modest lugs that easily transition from paved surfaces to uneven terrain.

results.name: Parley x Terrex Two Ultra 'Acid Mint'
EQT Primegreen 'Crew Blue'
results.story: The adidas EQT Primegreen ‘Crew Blue’ brings running shoe comfort to a spikeless golf shoe made with sustainability in mind. The waterproof upper, constructed from breathable mesh with no-sew synthetic overlays, incorporates recycled materials under the Primegreen banner. Lightweight cushioning arrives via a full-length Bounce midsole, enhanced with a Boost insert in the heel. Underfoot, the Adiwear rubber outsole features an integrated traction pattern for superior grip.

results.name: Multix Big Kid 'Black White'
results.story: The adidas Multix Big Kid ‘Black White’ pairs an essential color palette with a versatile silhouette built for play. The upper is constructed from breathable black mesh, reinforced with tonal no-sew skins and a synthetic leather heel overlay. A contrasting white adidas tag adorns the mesh tongue, matching the signature three-stripes that decorate the sneaker’s quarter panel. An Ortholite sockliner combines with a full-length EVA midsole to deliver cushioned comfort with every step.

results.name: Adilette Slide 'Halo Silver Solar Red'
results.story: The adidas Adilette Slide ‘Halo Silver Solar Red’ offers a simple two-tone colorway of the versatile slip-on. Constructed from quick-drying polyurethane, the textured bandage strap features a neutral grey finish with contrasting Solar Red three-stripes. A soft textile-lined interior combines with a contoured footbed to deliver step-in comfort. Lightweight cushioning is provided by an EVA midsole, accented with embossed adidas branding on the lateral sidewall.

results.name: S2G BOA 'White Grey'
results.story: The adidas S2G BOA ‘White Grey’ applies a neutral color scheme to a golf shoe built with running-shoe comfort. Recycled content is blended into the composition of the waterproof upper, featuring breathable textile with a durable polyurethane film. In lieu of traditional laces, the sneaker uses an innovative BOA Fit System that allows the wearer to dial in a precise fit. Lightweight cushioning is provided by a full-length Bounce midsole, reinforced underfoot by an Adiwear outsole with a V-shaped Traxion pattern.

results.name: Multix Little Kid 'Black White'
results.story: The adidas Multix Little Kid ‘Black White’ highlights an essential color palette on a versatile sneaker built for everyday wear. The breathable upper is constructed from black mesh, accented with contrasting white three-stripes and fortified with tonal fused overlays. An Ortholite sockliner works in concert with a pristine EVA midsole to deliver lightweight cushioning with every step. Underfoot, a matching white rubber outsole provides grippy traction.

results.name: Adizero Adios 5 'Black Silver Metallic'
results.story: A lightweight running shoe built for speed, the adidas Adizero Adios 5 ‘Black Silver Metallic’ features a midsole that combines springy Lightstrike cushioning with the energy-returning properties of Boost. Grippy Continental rubber is utilized on the two-part outsole, equipped with adidas’ Torsion System for enhanced midfoot stability. Up top, black Celermesh features single-layer construction that adapts to the wearer’s foot to deliver form-fitting comfort.

results.name: Terrex Free Hiker GTX 'Savanna'
results.story: The adidas Terrex Free Hiker GTX ‘Savanna’ showcases running-shoe comfort on an outdoor shoe engineered to take on the elements. A waterproof Gore-Tex membrane reinforces the beige Primeknit upper, featuring an elastic cuff and seamless abrasion-resistant overlays. Contrasting Hi-Res Yellow accents make their way to the signature three-stripes and webbing pull tab at the heel. Responsive cushioning is provided by a full-length Boost midsole, painted black and supported by a Continental rubber outsole.

results.name: Wmns Special 21 'Hazy Sky'
results.story: The adidas women’s Special 21 ‘Hazy Sky’ showcases vibrant hues on a lifestyle runner inspired by classic track shoes from the ‘80s. A bright teal hue distinguishes the traditional nylon and suede upper, built on a last that’s specific to a woman’s foot. adidas branding is inscribed in Hi-Res Yellow lettering on the leather heel overlay, matching the sneaker’s signature three-stripes and rubber outsole. The latter reinforces a full-length EVA midsole in a crisp white finish.

results.name: adidas T-Mac 2.0 EVO Paint Splatter
results.story: The adidas T-Mac 2 EVO ‘Paint Splatter’ showcases an eye-catching design on a modernized version of Tracy McGrady’s second signature shoe. A camo print in blue and yellow is applied to the textile tongue and collar, while a paint splatter effect enlivens the orange patent leather upper. The sneaker’s microperforated forefoot is rendered in a slightly darker orange finish and overlaid with molded TPU lines that wrap over the toe box. A painted camo-like print distinguishes the lightweight Bounce midsole.

results.name: adidas Harden Vol. 5 Futurenatural Core Black
adidas ZX 8000 Frozen Lemonade
results.story: The adidas ZX 8000 ‘Frozen Lemonade’ is taken from the brand’s ‘A-ZX Series,’ a sprawling 26-part release that celebrates the legacy of the ZX running franchise. Inspired by the ‘Citrus’ ZX colorway from the late ‘80s, the retro runner makes use of an off-white mesh upper with synthetic suede overlays in varying yellow shades. Removing the ice cube-print sockliner reveals an insole printed with a recipe for frozen lemonade. The sneaker rides on a lightweight EVA midsole, reinforced underfoot by a translucent rubber outsole.

results.name: X9000L4 'Chinese New Year - Year of the Ox'
adidas Ultra Boost 2021 Black Solar
results.story: The adidas UltraBoost 21 ‘Black Silver Metallic’ adds subtle neon accents to an otherwise neutral colorway of the brand’s flagship runner. ‘ULTRABOOST’ is printed in Solar Yellow lettering across the molded heel counter, adding rearfoot stability to a black and grey knit upper that incorporates Primeblue — recycled high-performance materials including Parley Ocean Plastic. Responsive cushioning arrives via a full-length Boost midsole, featuring an exaggerated heel curve that allows for the addition of more Boost capsules.

results.name: adidas Ultra Boost 2021 Grey White
results.story: The adidas UltraBoost 21 ‘Grey’ applies a monochromatic neutral finish to the lightweight and responsive performance running shoe. The sneaker’s breathable knit build, incorporating recycled Primeblue materials that include Parley Ocean Plastic, sits atop full-length Boost cushioning that packs 6% more Boost capsules than the UltraBoost 20. Underfoot, a revised Torsion system dubbed Linear Energy Push yields improved forefoot stiffness and energy return.

results.name: adidas Ultra Boost 2021 Solar Yellow Pink
results.story: The adidas UltraBoost 21 ‘Solar Yellow’ combines eye-catching style with lightweight and responsive performance. A fluorescent monochromatic finish is applied to a sock-like Primeknit upper that incorporates Parley Ocean Plastic and other recycled materials. Full-length Boost cushioning is supported by a Continental rubber outsole and a revised Torsion system dubbed Linear Energy Push, good for increased forefoot stiffness and enhanced energy return.

results.name: adidas Ultra Boost 2021 Core Black
results.story: The adidas UltraBoost 21 ‘Core Black’ applies a rudimentary palette to a performance running shoe that combines lightweight comfort with enhanced energy return. Recycled Primeblue materials, including Parley Ocean Plastic, goes into the construction of the knit upper, fortified with a midfoot cage and molded heel counte. An optimized Boost midsole, made with 6% more Boost capsules than the UltraBoost 20, features added responsiveness via a new Torsion system that adidas calls Linear Energy Push.
